title: Brasilia Wine Caffe
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Italian, Mediterranean, Fast food, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Take-out, European, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A small, traditional cafe in the city centre predominantly serving hot drinks, sandwiches, wine and cocktails. Displays the Italian 'Vegan OK' sign with information about its vegan cappuccino which is made using soya milk.
